Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\shad0\bord2\frz1.5\fs34\t(\fs32)\move(364.797,35,364.797,54,24,7323)\c&&HC9D4D7&}Warning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:03.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Viewers Sitting in Front of the Television,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.06,0:00:05.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the guys that appear in this anime are delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.23,0:00:07.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, please do not imitate what you see in this anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\b1\i0\bord0\blur0.3\fad(450,0)\c&HDADADA&\fs33\pos(362.532,49)}Do not imitate{\i1\fs40}!{\i0\fs33} Or this will happen{\i1\fs40}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}僕が泣いているのは とても悔しいからです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}Boku ga naite iru no wa totemo kuyashii kara desu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)}The reason I am crying is\Nbecause I am very frustrated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}人の尊さやさしさ 踏みにじられそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Hito no toutosa yasashisa fuminijiraresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.25,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}I feel as though the nobility and\Nkindness of man is being trampled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}力を示す者達は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Chikara o shimesu mono tachi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}しなやかさを失って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Shinayakasa o ushinatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:34.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Those who show their strength lose their grace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}ウソまみれドロまみれ じれったい風景でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uso-mamire doro-mamire jirettai fuukei desho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Covered in dirt and lies, isn't it a vexing sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}より強くしたたかに タフな生き方をしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Yori tsuyoku shitataka ni tafu na ikikata o shimashou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's live more strongly, fiercely, and tougher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}まっすぐ歩きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Massugu arukimasho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's walk straight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}風は向かい風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kaze wa mukai kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.94,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The wind is against us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ どけ どけ 後ろめたい奴はどけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke doke doke ushirometai yatsu wa doke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:58.78,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, move, move, those with\Na guilty conscience, move aside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}有象無象の町に 灯りをともせ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uzoumuzou no machi ni akari o tomose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.41,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Light up the town of riffraff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ そこ どけ 真実のお通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke soko doke shinjitsu no otouri da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.88,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, make way, truth is coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}正義の時代がくるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Seigi no jidai ga kuru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The era of justice will come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}希望の歌もあるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kibou no uta mo aru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}There are songs of hope too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}僕の命この世に 捧げてしまっていいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}Boku no inochi kono yo ni sasagete-shimatte ii sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)}I would happily sacrifice my life for this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:35.99,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\p1\shad0\blur1\c&H3298BA&\pos(343.272,318)}m -4 -5 l -7 -8 l -17 -4 l -11 4 l -16 15 l 0 11 l 14 16 l 11 3 l 19 -8 l 7 -9 l 0 -17 l -7 -8 l -4 -5 l 0 -11 l 3 -7 l 13 -5 l 7 1 l 10 11 l 0 8 l -10 11 l -7 2 l -12 -4
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:35.99,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\p1\shad0\blur1\c&H3298BA&\pos(490.551,322)}m -4 -5 l -7 -8 l -17 -4 l -11 4 l -16 15 l 0 11 l 14 16 l 11 3 l 19 -8 l 7 -9 l 0 -17 l -7 -8 l -4 -5 l 0 -11 l 3 -7 l 13 -5 l 7 1 l 10 11 l 0 8 l -10 11 l -7 2 l -12 -4
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:35.99,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)\blur1\shad0\fnArnold 2.1\fs46\c&HEBBC77&\pos(350.07,308)}Shooting   Star   Press
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.57,0:01:32.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"Let me say my name!"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.44,0:01:35.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hokuto's lackey's cry\N has not reached anyone as of yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.99,0:01:39.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Certainly, a meteorite falling on\Nthe school building is a big event.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.37,0:01:41.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I just need five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.12,0:01:44.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I want everyone to memorize my name.\NMy name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.45,0:01:47.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's trouble! Aliens came out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.21,0:01:48.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They're coming down this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.71,0:01:49.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Aliens...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.88,0:01:54.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How do you do, everyone.\N We're aliens. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.30,0:01:55.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now we'll introduce ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.51,0:01:57.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He said they'd introduce themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.22,0:01:57.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.72,0:01:58.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.51,0:02:03.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm a pitiful man who's lost the timing\Nto introduce himself for a variety of reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.89,0:02:07.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now I'll even settle for aliens!\NWould you hear my name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:08.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Understood. I shall hear your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:13.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Thanks. I knew aliens were sensible.\NEarthlings are hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.27,0:02:15.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now, please introduce yourself\Nto your satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.86,0:02:19.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then I'll tell you, alien. My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.07,0:02:20.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Captain, a ship has come for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:22.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's already time to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, then, everyone. Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:26.20,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What did they come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:28.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I couldn't say my name...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.21,0:02:31.96,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even to aliens...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.96,0:02:32.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Can I talk to you for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.71,0:02:37.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Listening to your conversation with the alien,\NI reflected on my actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:40.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm ashamed of myself as an Earthling.\NI'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:42.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I really want to hear your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.76,0:02:43.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:45.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Isn't that right, everyone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:52.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There's trouble!\N The aliens took Freddie by mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.98,0:02:55.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My... My name is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.23,0:03:01.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Moving right along, it's now the day\Nfor the Japan Boss Championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:04.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Badasses from all over Japan\Nhave gathered at Tokyo Dome.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.29,0:03:08.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.08,0:03:12.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's a rep from Hokkaido,\NBear Killer Kashiwabara!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:14.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I heard that he won a fight against a bear!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:17.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That one's a rep from Niigata,\NExterminator Takashiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:19.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,They said that he can talk with bears!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:23.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That guy is a rep from Kochi,\NPraise Heaper Okaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:25.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I heard that he raises a bear at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.35,0:03:26.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's meet in the finals!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? What did we talk about those guys for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:32.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We will now start the Japan Boss Championship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:34.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then, here is the first question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:38.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Milk is used to make yogurt. True or false?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.86,0:03:41.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That has nothing to do with being a boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:43.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please proceed to the true or false marker\Nthat matches your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:47.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Now, here is the answer.\NPlease look at the electric bulletin board.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:50.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The answer is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:55.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The winner is Mr. Kamiyama\Nfrom Cromartie High School!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.63,0:03:57.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The winner shouldn't\N be decided in the first round!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:00.09,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\c&H4AAABB&\3c&H2D688A&\be2\bord3\shad1\frz24.085\pos(569.854,125)\frx22\fry318}Destrade\N High School
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:00.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, did you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:03.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I heard that someone from Cromartie\Nhas won the Japan Boss Championship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.76,0:04:07.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!\N We've never heard of such a tournament!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.22,0:04:11.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's bull! We can't allow\N them to decide Japan's No. 1 Boss
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:13.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,without our, Des-High's, knowledge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.39,0:04:14.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.69,0:04:15.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yamaguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:19.86,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(365.93,392)}Noboru Yamaguchi (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.77,0:04:18.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Basically, all that's needed is for me to knock down the guy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.02,0:04:19.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,who won the tournament, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.36,0:04:21.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then, shall we go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.69,0:04:24.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh! Yamaguchi has finally gotten off his ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.53,0:04:26.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey! We're coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:29.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You guys are from Destrade High School!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:32.29,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You got some nerve coming to Cro-High!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:35.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I heard that Japan's No. 1 Boss is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:39.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Our boss, Yamaguchi, wants to fight with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:43.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm Yamaguchi. Where's the one\N people call the strongest boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:44.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:45.43,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\an1\pos(73.639,340)}Takashi Kamiyama (16) No. 1 Boss in Japan\N (Pen Name - Honey Boy)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.88,0:04:45.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:47.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Honey!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.51,0:04:51.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second. Why is such\Na puny guy the toughest boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:53.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's what I wanna know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.52,0:04:56.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I suppose you have various complaints,\Nbut I'm the champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.36,0:05:01.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Yamaguchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:04.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see, that's what it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:09.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In short, the Boss Championship was actually\Na tournament to select the best comedian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.37,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fnAnna\fs30\pos(175.601,53)\c&H381126&\3c&H3D3123&\bord3\shad0\t(\3c&H90494C&)}Japan Comedian Championship
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:09.28,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnAnna\fs30\pos(175.601,53)\c&H381126&\3c&H90494C&\bord3\shad0}Japan Comedian Championship
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In short, the Boss Championship was actually\Na tournament to select the best comedian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:13.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And this genius postcard artisan\Nbecame the champion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:15.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If that's the case, I can understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.67,0:05:18.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then I definitely can't back out of this fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:21.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right! Why don't we start the fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Are you insane?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.26,0:05:24.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Are you seriously going to fight\Nwith a guy like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.63,0:05:27.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I understand. I'll accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.72,0:05:30.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then, let's start!
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please press the button quickly\Nwhen you know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:32.97,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord25\fs27\fnAnna\shad0\frx22\fry44\c&HFFE7E5&\3c&H701D12&\frz335.029\clip(m 90.625 423 l 99.75 486 333.125 505 211.875 489)\org(211,516)\pos(179,547)}Crossing America\NBoss Quiz
