Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.43,0:05:34.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,A quiz?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.85,0:05:36.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I thought we came here to fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:38.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but by the time we realized it,\Nwe were forced into this quiz game.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:42.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Just as you'd expect from Honey Boy.\NWhat a funny turn of events.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:44.07,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Moreover, while saying stuff like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:46.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I noticed myself wearing a contestant's silk hat
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:48.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and I'm so funny that\N I want to poke fun at myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:53.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh well, I'll give in and say\N it's okay to play the quiz match, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:56.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why are you the MC\N when we came to fight against you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:57.83,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Here's the first question!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:06:00.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Ignoring the stupid question\Nthat won't go anywhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:02.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Just as you'd expect from Honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:05.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Not only does he know how to make people\Nlaugh, but he also knows how to run the event.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:09.97,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an7\p1\shad0\bord0\c&H611910&\pos(391.987,347)}m 0 0 l 180 -15 145 70 -30 85{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:09.97,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs29\fnAnna\shad0\c&HFFE7E5&\3c&H611910&\clip(m 388.625 346 l 362.5 425 556.25 413 592.5 334)\org(369,449)\frz11.577\pos(474.69,403)\frx318\fry26}Crossing America\NBoss Quiz
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:09.97,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an7\p1\shad0\c&HD0D0D0&\bord0\pos(354.601,439)}m 0 0 l 175 -18 155 27 -14 45{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:09.97,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs29\fnAnna\shad0\c&H393939&\frz11.577\frx318\fry26\clip(m 354.625 440 l 343.25 483 523.375 466 549.5 423)\org(363,496)\pos(446.367,482)}Question\N Collection
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.80,0:06:09.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,After the latest member change of the popular group Morning Musume, which phase are they in now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:12.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sixth phase!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:13.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:14.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:20.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Idiot! In the comedy world,\Ncorrect answers are worthless!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:22.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How much you make people\Nlaugh is the important point.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:25.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In short, to us,\N "a laugh is the correct answer."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:35.41,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an9\p1\shad0\c&H701C13&\bord0\pos(381.791,446)}m 0 0 l 250 -120 255 20 25 150{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:35.41,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs38\fnAnna\shad0\c&HFFE7E5&\3c&H611910&\frz28.023\frx346\fry22\org(308,479)\pos(297.956,464)}Crossing America\NBoss Quiz
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:29.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,These words might be remembered by\Nlater generations if I become famous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:33.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then, here's the second question:\N1.41421356 is the square root of 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then what is 1.7320508?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:37.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mr. Hayashida!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:39.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:42.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's it! That's what\N the viewers are looking for!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.50,0:06:45.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I almost made a snappy comeback saying,\N"Don't press the button if you don't know!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.84,0:06:47.34,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.34,0:06:50.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If I make a comeback, his joke will stick out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.26,0:06:52.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If that happens, I'm getting \Nthe short end of the stick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:55.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Smart stupidity that almost\N made me make a comeback.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:58.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This mohawk guy is no ordinary man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:07:02.77,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an9\p1\shad0\c&H701C13&\bord0\pos(381.791,446)}m 0 0 l 250 -120 255 20 25 150{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:07:02.77,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs38\fnAnna\shad0\c&HFFE7E5&\3c&H611910&\frz28.023\frx346\fry22\org(308,479)\pos(297.956,464)}Crossing America\NBoss Quiz
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:07:00.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then here's the third question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:02.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How many total prefectures are there in Japan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:07.69,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an9\p1\shad0\bord0\c&H6D1C15&\pos(314.949,406)}m 0 0 l 50 -20 45 10 -3 30{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:07.69,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an9\p1\shad0\bord0\c&HEFEFF0&\pos(309.285,442)}m 0 0 l 50 -20 45 0 -3 20{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:07.69,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs12\fnAnna\shad0\c&HFFE7E5&\3c&H611910&\frx340\fry36\frz20.288\org(228,440)\pos(300.222,438)}Crossing America\NBoss Quiz
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:07.69,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs11\fnAnna\shad0\c&H393939&\frx340\fry36\frz20.288\org(237,492)\pos(292.291,463)}Question\N Collection
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:04.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mr. Hayashida!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:07.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I just got the answer to the earlier question.\NCan I answer to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:08.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, you can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.74,0:07:11.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's prolonging the earlier stupidity well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.16,0:07:14.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Does that mean that the earlier stuff was\Na precursor, and well-calculated stupidity?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.66,0:07:16.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then, here's the last question.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:20.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,By the way, answering the last question correctly earns you three million points!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:23.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then what were those questions up to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.38,0:07:25.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see... It's a little ordinary,
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.54,0:07:28.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but a standard theory\N in comedy quiz shows. Good job, Honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:32.09,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an9\p1\shad0\c&H701C13&\bord0\pos(381.791,446)}m 0 0 l 250 -120 255 20 25 150{\p0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:32.09,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord0\fs38\fnAnna\shad0\c&HFFE7E5&\3c&H611910&\frz28.023\frx346\fry22\org(308,479)\pos(297.956,464)}Crossing America\NBoss Quiz
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:30.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Please listen carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.30,0:07:32.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,About thirty years ago, in Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.72,0:07:37.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's up to my comical answer now, after all,\Nin order to liven up the end and finish this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:40.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What should I do? If I have to choose\None out of three, I'll say number four...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:42.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But no, that's mediocre.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:44.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then I can answer before the question...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:46.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But it won't work if no one\N makes a snappy comeback saying
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.40,0:07:48.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"the question wasn't given yet!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:52.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In short, a dumb answer that doesn't need\Na snappy comeback is the only way to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:57.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Moreover, I'll have to lower my joke level\Nto match this low-level audience,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:07:59.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,which leaves me no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:01.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yes, Mr. Yamaguchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.54,0:08:03.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Gachoooon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:04.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:05.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:10.88,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\fad(500,0)}Yamaguchi gets three million points!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.17,0:08:10.88,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:11.92,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnDupree\fs24\pos(453.165,279)\frz348.5\frx13\fry30\bord0\c&H443128&\blur0.5}Southern
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:11.92,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnDupree\fs24\pos(461.095,310)\frz349\frx13\fry30\bord0\c&H443128&\blur0.5}Wind
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What do you want,\N calling me out to a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.93,0:08:17.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Actually, there's something that\NI want to talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.39,0:08:18.93,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Are you worried about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.47,0:08:21.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm having a hard time saying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:24.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Just say it. While I may look like this,\NI'm actually tight-lipped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:27.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. Well, in your case,\Nrather than being tight-lipped,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:30.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I also figure that you'll forget it by tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.15,0:08:33.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, I'm very\Nsusceptible to motion sickness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:35.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What? Motion sickness?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:40.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I, Takenouchi, am this big, but I'm not good\Nwith transportation because I get sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:42.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:44.33,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's motion sickness?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.33,0:08:47.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?! You're asking what it is?\NYou're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:49.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I mean, you don't know\N what motion sickness is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:53.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I don't understand the feeling of getting sick\Nwhen you're riding in something at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.72,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Is it a disease?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.72,0:08:56.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not really a disease, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:59.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's why you're so fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.10,0:09:00.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You really don't understand, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:03.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In any case, it wouldn't look good\Nif Takenouchi, a boss at Cro-High,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:06.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,gets motion sickness, would it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:10.69,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wanna conquer that problem\N before people find out about it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:13.28,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a rigid way of thinking\Nabout the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:17.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You don't wanna be seen looking so pitiful,\Nsince you're the boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.11,0:09:19.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Aren't those psychological burdens\Ngiving you pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.99,0:09:21.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,and causing you to feel sick or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.83,0:09:25.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You suddenly said\N something decent, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.00,0:09:28.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You could get sick due to the load on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:32.84,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But after talking to me like this,\Ndon't you feel a little better?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:35.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Come to think of it,\NI'm starting to feel much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.97,0:09:38.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,After all, it's not good to have a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.43,0:09:40.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's best to talk about it with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.72,0:09:43.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I had something\Nthat I was worried about,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:46.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but while listening to your story, I started\Nthinking that it was silly to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:50.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Really? I didn't think that even you'd have\Nsomething that you were worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.06,0:09:52.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Say it. I won't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.15,0:09:54.78,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm relieved to hear that. Then I'll tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.74,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I'm wearing a wig.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:10:01.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, compared to your concern,\Nmine may not be that much of a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.45,0:10:04.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No, I don't care about my concern any more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.37,0:10:06.75,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To tell you the truth, my parents are very strict.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:10.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All my brothers are elites.\NI guess it's a reaction to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:13.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,When I noticed, I was in the world of badasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.21,0:10:16.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But I'm afraid of my parents,\Nso I can't quite be decisive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:18.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So I'm still keeping this hairstyle at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.59,0:10:21.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No matter how bad you are,\Nyou absolutely must obey your parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.43,0:10:26.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But if you wore a suit,\Nyou'd look just like a businessman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:29.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Actually, I've seen you in town a couple of times when I was looking like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.77,0:10:31.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,though you probably didn't realize it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:33.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kamiyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:35.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This isn't good! You'd better\Nput your wig on quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:36.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I dropped my wig!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.44,0:10:37.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What are you doing? Quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:38.95,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Forget it! I'll get it for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:41.41,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right!
