Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.21,0:11:36.42,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sakigake!! Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:41.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's time for Takashi Kamiyama's\Nsame old familiar one point living course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.09,0:11:42.38,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,For the Electric Mandolin's year of manufacture,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:44.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,specs are more important\Nthan the serial number.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:48.89,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Oh? Freddie! You're back from outer space.
